# StreamYourCare Commands

#### Needs

* **Broadcasting Software**: OBS for Windows ([Download](https://obsproject.com/download))

* **Livestream ChatBot**: Streamer.Bot ([Download](https://streamer.bot/downloads))

## Streamer.Bot
- Open the Import Dialog by clicking ```Import``` on the top toolbar of Streamer.Bot
![streamer.bot](/streamyourcare/docs/img/sbimport.png)
- In the **Import Dialog**, paste the import string into the ```Import String``` input.
- Click ```Import``` when you are ready to complete your import.
- ```Enable``` all commands via ```Right-Click < Enable``` on the commands you want to use.

### All Commands
```

```

### BRB
```!brb``` toggles to Privacy Overlay
```

```
### BACK
```!back``` toggles from Privacy Overlay back to Webcam (Scene) in OBS
```

```
### CENSOR
```!censor {time}``` censors the stream with Privacy Overlay for ```{time}``` ms.
```

```
### checkinCaution
Sends ```"I'm having a difficult time, notifying staff @ {time}"``` in Twitch chat.
```

```
### checkinOkay 
Sends ```"{name} sent I'm Okay! Be back soon, standby at {time}"``` in Twitch chat.
```

```
### checkinRequest
Sends ```"Can you check in on me in the next 5 minutes? The time is now {time}"``` in chat.
```

```
### toggleCam
```!cam``` Toggles camera on/off with timestamped chat alert.
```

```
### startSubtitles
```!subs``` Opens Windows ```"Live Captions"``` program for subtitles.
```

```
### startRecording
Starts recording on OBS
```

```
### stopRecording
Stops recording on OBS
```

```
### startStreaming
Starts streaming on OBS
```

```
### stopStreaming
Stops streaming on OBS
```

```
### toggleOBS
Toggles focus on OBS window to check what your broadcast looks like.
```

```

## Voice Commands

### All Voice Commands
```

```

### voicePrivacy
Toggles privacy overlay 
```

```
### voiceFalseAlarm
Sends ```"{name} sent 'False alarm, I'm okay!'``` at {time}
```

```
### voiceBRB
Another voice privacy overlay toggle 
```

```
### voiceBack
Toggle back to webcam (Scene) in OBS
```

```
### voiceBack2
Delayed toggle back to webcam (Scene) in OBS
```

```
### voiceChatShield
Enable Shield Chat mode with ```"Safe Talking"``` Voice Command
```

```
### voiceSlowmodeOn/voiceSlowmodeOff 
Toggles ```Slowmode Chat``` with ```"Slowmode Activate"``` and ```"Slowmode Off"```
```

```
### voiceAssistant 
Enable Windows ```"Voice Access"``` with ```"VoiceAccess"``` Voice Command
```

```
